<paragraph id="391AA5FD4F34CA49BFF9521F45E1A397" pageId="null" pageNumber="791">
Unterscheidet sich von der Gattung 
<taxonomicName id="AC9C33C4E037FFF1C0CE8780F5C46C14" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="Gypsophila" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="null" pageNumber="791" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B154B4A5DC563C9DCB32E5D1CA970A2A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="791">Gypsophila</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(S. 787) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<emphasis id="17E6D25261294B1AED8A5F4FB1EC5D02" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="791">
Kelch zur Fruchtzeit aufgeblasen, scharf 5kantig, ohne 
<normalizedToken id="229734AD5BA00AE75C14EDB72528A3D8" originalValue="trockenhäutige" pageId="null" pageNumber="791">trockenhaeutige</normalizedToken>
Streifen.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="EAFB3A96CD89BBBDAA3C841EF5046E7E" pageId="null" pageNumber="791">
Die Gattung 
<emphasis id="3D0481B55D9B7029D428A7029FA6DBE1" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="791">
<taxonomicName id="5CF077467E82D31F3A8824D68B6FDFA6" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="Vaccaria" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="null" pageNumber="791" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Vaccaria</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="B0A98E5BCEAF38CD29EAAF86E9DC9823" originalValue="umfaβt" pageId="null" pageNumber="791">umfaβt</normalizedToken>
4 Arten, von denen 3 nur in Vorderasien vorkommen.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
